.DT
sayto
$MUDNAME$ player help
sayto

.SH Name
.SI 5
sayto - Direct a say to someone in the room.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
sayto <person> <text>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Sayto sends the message to all the people in the room and also makes the
message look directed.  With a normal say you would see:

Windy says: hello

With sayto you would see:

Windy says to Shiannar: hello
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> sayto shiannar hello
> sayto drem The sun shines out of your eyes and drowns me in sweet surprise.
> sayto gototh Whooo!  Look at that coffee table!  The inlay!
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
emote, ssay, lsay, shout, tell, whisper, sayto.
.EI
